      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AUNTY FAYE (4) was below best at her last start when 6th at The Meadows following a second place finish (30.57) there two back. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Can make amends. FRED THE FOX (3) showed strong pace early from the inside rail and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing fourth over 450m Ballarat in 25.86. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Cannot be left out. PEAKY COLLINDA (2) placed three back at Ballarat then out of the placings last couple but moves to box 2 this time where he has performed well. Expected to do much better this time. LES NORTON (6) should be thereabouts.",
